==============================================================================
  Release of version 0.01 of Parse::VB
==============================================================================


NAME

    Parse::VB - Parse VB source file


DESCRIPTION

    VB parse a Visual Basic Source Files for different usage.
    Thanks to this module, people can make VB to Html documentation
    of the source files.
    It is also possible to check programming rules. (variable naming, declarations, comments..)

    VB recognize :
    	
    	Methods
    	Functions
    	Properties
    	Variable declaration

LIMITATIONS

    * There's no support for parsing directly from an input stream.

    * The generator doesn't handle left-recursion.


PREREQUISITES

    Parse::VB requires RecDescent 1.80 or greater.
    

INSTALLATION

    It's all pure Perl, so just put the .pm files in their appropriate
    local Perl subdirectories.


CHANGES AND FUTURE DEVELOPMENT

    no ideas of what can be improved for further versions..

